# Broker / Execution Rules

Use the `futu-order-execution` skill when editing these files.

## Futu HK defaults

- `SecurityFirm.FUTUSECURITIES`
- OpenD: `127.0.0.1:11111`
- HK codes: `HK.00700` | US codes: `US.AAPL`

## Safety

- Never hardcode `FUTU_TRADE_PASSWORD`
- Never default `trd_env` to REAL
- Log order_id on success; log full error on failure
- Quote subscription belongs in `src/data/`, not broker

## Do not add here

- Indicators, SMA, signal generation
- Strategy-specific logic
